@startuml ZMQ RPC Metrics - PR#793 Ground Truth
!pragma teoz true
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam actorBorderColor #666666
skinparam lifelineBorderColor #666666
skinparam lifelineBackgroundColor #F5F5F5

title **ZMQ RPC Metrics - PR#793 MetaPb 传递 & Tick 记录机制**

participant "Client Thread" as C <<Client>>
participant "ZmqStubImpl\nAsyncWriteImpl" as SI <<StubImpl>>
participant "MsgQue\noutBound queue" as MQ <<MsgQue>>
participant "MsgQueMgr\nPrefetcher" as PM <<Prefetcher>>
participant "ZmqFrontend\nSendMsg" as FE <<Frontend>>
database "Network" as Net
participant "ZmqService" as S <<Server>>
participant "WorkerEntry" as W <<Worker>>
participant "ServerUnaryWriterReaderImpl\nWrite" as SW <<ServerStream>>
participant "Business Handler" as H <<Handler>>
participant "ZmqServerImpl\nServiceToClient" as SImpl <<ServerImpl>>

note across
  **Client Ticks** (zmq_constants.h)
  - CLIENT_ENQUEUE: 消息放入 outBound queue (zmq_stub_impl.h L167)
  - CLIENT_STUB_SEND: mQue->SendMsg() 返回后 (zmq_stub_impl.h L169)
  - CLIENT_DEQUEUE: prefetcher 从队列取出消息 (zmq_msg_queue.h L682)
  - CLIENT_ZMQ_SEND: zmq_msg_send 成功后 (zmq_msg_queue.h L728)

  **Server Ticks**
  - SERVER_RECV: zmq_msg_recv 返回后 (zmq_service.cpp L1198)
  - SERVER_DEQUEUE: 从 worker 队列取出 (zmq_service.cpp L723)
  - SERVER_EXEC_END: 业务 handler 完成 (zmq_server_stream_base.h L374)
  - SERVER_ZMQ_SEND: zmq_msg_send 成功后 (zmq_server_impl.cpp L187) ✓ 已实现

  **注意**: TICK_SERVER_SEND 已移除（被 SERVER_ZMQ_SEND 替代）
end note

== Client: 发送请求 & MetaPb 构造 ==

C -> SI : rpc_call(req)
activate C
note over SI: 1. 创建 **请求 MetaPb**\n包含 client ticks

SI -> SI : RecordTick(meta, CLIENT_ENQUEUE)
note over SI: **CLIENT_ENQUEUE** (L167)

SI -> MQ : mQue->SendMsg(p)  // meta 被 moved 到 queue
note over MQ: 2. **请求 meta 已在 outBound queue**\n**CLIENT_STUB_SEND** (L169)

SI -> SI : clientMeta = meta  // 复制一份用于后续 merge
note over SI: 3. **复制请求 MetaPb**\n存储在 AsyncCallBack 中

deactivate C

== Prefetcher: 异步发送 ==

MQ -> PM : prefetcher 取消息
activate PM

note over PM: 4. **CLIENT_DEQUEUE** (L682)\n从队列取出

PM -> FE : routeFn_(msg)
FE -> Net : zmq_msg_send()
note over PM: 5. **CLIENT_ZMQ_SEND** (L728)\n但这个 tick 无法传回给 clientMeta！

deactivate PM

== Network Transport ==

Net -> S : TCP/UDS

== Server: 接收 & 处理 ==

activate S
note over S: 6. **SERVER_RECV** (L1198)
deactivate S

S -> W : WorkerEntry()
activate S
note over S: 7. **SERVER_DEQUEUE** (L723)

W -> H : handler(req)
activate W

H --> W : rsp
deactivate H

W -> SW : Write(rsp)
deactivate W
activate SW

note over SW: 8. **SERVER_EXEC_END** (L374)\n业务逻辑完成

deactivate SW
deactivate S

== Server: 发送回复 & MetaPb 构造 ==

note over SImpl: 9. **构造回复 MetaPb**\n使用**请求 MetaPb** (来自 WorkerEntry)

SImpl -> SImpl : RecordTick(meta, SERVER_ZMQ_SEND)
note over SImpl: **SERVER_ZMQ_SEND** (L187)

SImpl -> SImpl : RecordServerLatencyMetrics(meta)
note over SImpl: 计算 SERVER_QUEUE_WAIT,\nSERVER_EXEC, SERVER_REPLY

SImpl -> SImpl : PushFrontProtobufToFrames(meta, frames)
note over SImpl: 10. **序列化 meta 到 frames**\nticks 被包含在序列化后的数据中

SImpl -> Net : zmq_msg_send()

== Client: 接收回复 & MetaPb Merge ==

Net -> C : TCP/UDS
activate C

note over C: 11. **CLIENT_RECV** (zmq_stub_impl.h L238)

C -> C : rsp.first (回复 MetaPb)
note over C: 12. **回复 meta 包含:**\n- SERVER ticks (RECV, DEQUEUE, EXEC_END, ZMQ_SEND)\n- SERVER_EXEC_NS (计算后的值)\n- 但**没有** CLIENT_ZMQ_SEND！

C -> C : asyncCall->GetClientMeta()
note over C: 13. 获取存储的 **clientMeta**\n(包含 CLIENT_ENQUEUE, CLIENT_STUB_SEND, CLIENT_DEQUEUE)

C -> C : Merge ticks
note over C: 14. **合并 clientMeta ticks 到 rsp.first**\n然后计算 E2E/NETWORK metrics

deactivate C

== Metrics 公式 (当前实现) ==

note across
  **Client:**
  - CLIENT_QUEUING = CLIENT_ZMQ_SEND - CLIENT_ENQUEUE ❌ **MISSING** (CLIENT_ZMQ_SEND 无法获取)
  - CLIENT_STUB_SEND = CLIENT_DEQUEUE - CLIENT_STUB_SEND ✓

  **Server:**
  - SERVER_QUEUE_WAIT = SERVER_DEQUEUE - SERVER_RECV ✓
  - SERVER_EXEC = SERVER_EXEC_END - SERVER_DEQUEUE ✓ (但值偏大，可能需检查)
  - SERVER_REPLY = SERVER_ZMQ_SEND - SERVER_EXEC_END ✓

  **E2E:**
  - E2E = CLIENT_RECV - CLIENT_ENQUEUE ✓
  - NETWORK = E2E - SERVER_EXEC ✓
end note

== 已知问题 ==

note across
  **Issue #1: CLIENT_ZMQ_SEND 无法获取**
  - 原因: SendDirect 在 prefetcher 线程运行，clientMeta 存储在 AsyncWriteImpl 线程
  - 影响: CLIENT_QUEUING metric MISSING
  - 状态: 架构限制，待重构

  **Issue #2: SERVER_EXEC 值偏大 (930us)**
  - 现状: 平均 930us，max 424ms
  - 需检查: SERVER_EXEC_END 和 SERVER_DEQUEUE 是否在同一执行路径
  - 状态: 需分析

  **Issue #3: MetaPb 传递机制不清晰**
  - 请求 meta 和回复 meta 是不同对象
  - SERVER ticks 需要通过回复 meta 传递给 client
  - 当前设计: 先记录 tick，再序列化 (在 ZmqServerImpl::ServiceToClient 中)
end note

@enduml
